objects.name: SKILLZ Street Quiz!

questions.question: Fact or Nonsense: You can talk with your SKILLZ Street coach about important things in your life.

answers.response: Remember, you can always talk to your SKILLZ Street Coach about important things in your life.
Correct! It's a fact! Remember, you can always talk to your SKILLZ Street Coach about important things in your life.

questions.question: Fact or Nonsense: You can dial Coach Tumi to get important information about health services and youth centres in Soweto.

answers.response: Aybo wena!! It's a fact! Dial Coach Tumi to get important information about health services and youth centres in Soweto
Correct! It's a fact! Dial Coach Tumi to get important information about health services and youth centres in Soweto.

questions.question: Fact or Nonsense: SKILLZ Street coaches are the coolest!

answers.response: Aish, sisi! It's a fact! Your SKILLZ Street Coaches are role models in their communities. Talk with them to learn about how YOU can be a role model too!

questions.question: Fact or Nonsense: You will play netball in SKILLZ Street.
